 - Come on, let's move these things.

255
00:15:34,380 --> 00:15:37,360
Does Ms. Qiao often treat everyone with these, too?

256
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:39,020
 Reminder number one. 

257
00:15:39,020 --> 00:15:40,979
 Qiao Jingjing and Zhou Xiaoqi haven't gotten along for many years. 

258
00:15:40,979 --> 00:15:44,220
 You must handle their relationship carefully. 

259
00:15:44,220 --> 00:15:47,220
Well... Ms. Qiao did as well.

260
00:15:47,220 --> 00:15:49,920
All right. I'll take you to the director to say hi.

261
00:15:49,920 --> 00:15:52,879
- Sure. 
 - Okay, come on.

262
00:15:54,820 --> 00:15:56,820
Jingjing.

263
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:01,070
Qiqi.

264
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:02,920
 Round 1. 

265
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,440
Jingjing.

266
00:16:08,979 --> 00:16:11,100
It's been a while, I missed you so much.

267
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:12,961
- I'm sorry. 
 - It's fine.

268
00:16:12,961 --> 00:16:14,979
I think you were too excited.

269
00:16:14,979 --> 00:16:17,099
You look great.

270
00:16:17,099 --> 00:16:20,799
After being in the desert for so long, your skin is still so moisturized.

271
00:16:20,799 --> 00:16:23,840
 I rarely have a pimple, and you saw it so quickly. 

272
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:27,560
My dear, I miss you so much. You're finally here.

273
00:16:27,560 --> 00:16:30,410
Did you become slimmer again?

274
00:16:30,410 --> 00:16:32,259
Your waist is so small.

275
00:16:32,259 --> 00:16:35,079
 I only gained 4 pounds in two years, and my waist increased by 2cm. 

276
00:16:35,079 --> 00:16:37,759
 Can Qiao Jingjing tell? 

277
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:43,990
 Round 2. 

278
00:17:27,519 --> 00:17:30,460
 If you kill me, soldiers will still chase after you. 

279
00:17:30,460 --> 00:17:32,320
 Give me what I want. 

280
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:35,599
 Perhaps your life might be spared. 

281
00:17:35,599 --> 00:17:37,759
 Stop following me. 

282
00:17:45,097 --> 00:17:47,199
Cut. Thank you.

283
00:17:47,199 --> 00:17:48,890
The look in Jingjing's eyes is perfect.

284
00:17:48,890 --> 00:17:50,790
Xiaoqi isn't bad, either.

285
00:17:59,020 --> 00:18:02,659
How did Qiao Jingjing improve so much?

286
00:18:02,659 --> 00:18:05,340
She's usually so dramatic and pretentious.

287
00:18:05,340 --> 00:18:07,599
I thought that she wouldn't be able to play this character well.

288
00:18:07,599 --> 00:18:10,860
I didn't expect that once she's in character, she has great aura.

289
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:13,020
She almost suppressed mine.

290
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:15,299
She still wasn't able to suppress you, right?

291
00:18:15,299 --> 00:18:18,179
Besides, I think your acting is way better than hers.

292
00:18:18,179 --> 00:18:22,339
Sister, do you want to look at the script and ponder upon it more?

293
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:29,100
Sister, Mr. Chen said that he wants to visit you on set.

294
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:34,580
Really? Are you visiting me?

295
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:47,980
Ms. Xiaoqi.

296
00:18:47,980 --> 00:18:50,519
You're so thoughtful. Look, everyone is eating so happily.

297
00:18:50,519 --> 00:18:53,080
If everyone is happy, I'm happy.

298
00:18:55,260 --> 00:18:58,320
There is a lot of delicious food. Shouldn't we thank Ms. Xiaoqi?

299
00:18:58,320 --> 00:19:00,280
- Not bad. 
 - Let's thank Ms. Xiaoqi together.

300
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:03,539
- This looks extravagant. 
 - Thank you, Ms. Xiaoqi.

301
00:19:03,539 --> 00:19:06,439
Don't be shy. Eat more.

302
00:19:07,819 --> 00:19:10,639
Director. Do you want to eat something over there?

303
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:14,520
Get lost.

304
00:19:35,020 --> 00:19:36,740
Jingjing.

305
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:40,060
Zhou Xiaoqi's assistant sent some food over.

306
00:19:41,139 --> 00:19:42,700
Did you thank her?

307
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:46,280
Of course. I know my manners.

308
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:48,379
There is a lot of food.

309
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:51,500
They're all oily and salty.

310
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:54,028
I can't eat them late at night.

311
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:57,579
Are you still thinking about food?

312
00:19:57,579 --> 00:20:00,280
Aren't you worried at all?

313
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:04,140
- About what? 
 - Teacher Yu is coming to visit you.

314
00:20:04,819 --> 00:20:07,960
What should I worry about? I don't have a kissing scene for this project.

315
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,539
I'm not talking about that.

316
00:20:09,539 --> 00:20:14,088
Zhou Xiaoqi's boyfriend came before Teacher Yu, and he brought so much food.

317
00:20:14,088 --> 00:20:18,540
Barbecue, spicy hot pot, snacks. And he even invited a chef.

318
00:20:18,540 --> 00:20:21,360
Teacher Yu can't get defeated.

319
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:26,859
If you're craving food, eat. Don't waste Zhou Xiaoqi's food.

320
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:30,980
Who's craving food? I'm worried.

321
00:20:34,399 --> 00:20:39,460
What if we ask Teacher Yu to bring stuff for the crew too and reimburse it from Sister Ling?

322
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:42,165
We can't lose to Zhou Xiaoqi on this aspect.

323
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:48,859
Xiao Zhu. At a young age, why are you so competitive?

324
00:20:48,859 --> 00:20:52,981
Don't you always say that you must be prettier than Zhou Xiaoqi?

325
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:03,660
Today, what Zhou Xiaoqi's boyfriend did was too exaggerated.

326
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:06,281
Didn't you notice that the director was unhappy?

327
00:21:07,339 --> 00:21:09,420
He delayed our filming.

328
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:11,900
If someone does that again, the director will be furious.

329
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:15,800
That's why it's better for Teacher Yu to come and leave quietly.

330
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:22,720
Besides, when I usually ask you who's prettier between me and Zhou Xiaoqi,

331
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:25,579
I was just joking. Don't take me seriously.

332
00:21:25,579 --> 00:21:27,859
Why should we compare our boyfriends? Look at the practice now.

333
00:21:27,859 --> 00:21:29,980
If I want to compete with her, I'll do it with projects.

334
00:21:29,980 --> 00:21:34,360
Besides, Teacher Yu is so smart, talented, handsome, and chic.

335
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:38,460
Did I use him to suppress others? No.

336
00:21:38,460 --> 00:21:42,180
Because being talented myself is the most important thing.

337
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:48,640
That's why it's enough for me to be prettier than her.

338
00:21:53,379 --> 00:21:57,800
If you didn't use so many adjectives and that last thing you said, I almost believed you.

339
00:21:58,660 --> 00:22:01,379
You're right. Don't waste the food.

340
00:22:05,239 --> 00:22:08,700
Jingjing, when is Teacher Yu coming?

341
00:22:09,600 --> 00:22:12,160
In three days, around 11 a.m.

342
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:14,760
- Where is he coming from? Shanghai? 
 - I don't know.

343
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:18,080
He didn't tell me where he went on his business trip this time. I think it's confidential.

344
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:22,559
Anyway, don't aerospace workers perform experiments in places like the Gobi Desert?

345
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:27,819
When he comes in three days, I should be filming. Help me pick him up.

346
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:50,600
I wonder where he'll be coming from.

347
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:02,441
 I'm still very worried. 

348
00:23:06,777 --> 00:23:08,919
 What's the matter? 

349
00:23:08,919 --> 00:23:12,801
 Teacher Yu is coming for a visit today. I'm waiting for him. 

350
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:17,739
 Isn't that a good thing? Jingjing and Teacher Yu haven't seen each other for a long time. 

351
00:23:17,739 --> 00:23:21,259
 But two days ago, Zhou Xiaoqi's boyfriend came for a visit. He made a big deal with his arrival. 

352
00:23:21,259 --> 00:23:24,680
 If Teacher Yu comes here empty-handed, they'll surely criticize him behind his back. 

353
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:28,600
 I really don't want to see Zhou Xiaoqi's assistant look so pleased. 

354
00:24:45,612 --> 00:24:48,563
Xiao Zhu, it's been a while.

355
00:24:51,380 --> 00:24:53,661
Teacher Yu, it's been a while.

356
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:05,080
I'll bring you over.

357
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:12,840
 You might not receive this now, but I must tell you. 

358
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:15,920
 It's useless no matter how exaggerated Zhou Xiaoqi's boyfriend was. We won. 

359
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:19,620
 Teacher Yu's long legs and army boots made an instant kill. 

360
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:22,160
Jingjing, I think we should do another take

361
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:25,810
of you crawling and lifting your head in the desert, okay?

362
00:25:25,810 --> 00:25:27,130
The look in your eyes is right,

363
00:25:27,130 --> 00:25:30,170
- but I hope that your entire body movement has more tension. 
 - Okay?

364
00:25:30,170 --> 00:25:31,420
- Okay. 
 - Thank you.

365
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:33,820
Thank you, Director.

366
00:25:50,539 --> 00:25:52,139
Let's do it when you're ready.

367
00:25:55,020 --> 00:25:57,240
Scene 38, shot 3, take 2. 
    

368
00:26:06,700 --> 00:26:09,400
Cut. That's a good take.

369
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:11,160
The director said that we could rest for one hour.

370
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:13,330
Everyone can relax a bit.

371
00:26:13,339 --> 00:26:15,670
Director. This one is fine, right?

372
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:17,740
Yes, take a look.

373
00:26:17,740 --> 00:26:20,059
- What do you think? Are you satisfied? 
 - It's good, I'm quite satisfied.

374
00:26:20,059 --> 00:26:22,239
- All right. Thank you, then... 
 - Okay.

375
00:26:22,239 --> 00:26:24,400
- Rest a bit, okay? 
 - Okay.

376
00:27:11,259 --> 00:27:13,079
I missed you so much.

377
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:21,299
Sister.

378
00:27:21,299 --> 00:27:23,260
Is that Qiao Jingjing's boyfriend?

379
00:27:23,260 --> 00:27:25,759
She doesn't care about people seeing them at all.

380
00:27:25,759 --> 00:27:27,714
He's so hand...

381
00:27:29,940 --> 00:27:33,020
He's all right.

382
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:36,560
Isn't he the one who works at the Aerospace Research Institute?

383
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:39,680
They've been together for two years and photographed many times.

384
00:27:50,840 --> 00:27:52,479
Let me check.

385
00:27:52,479 --> 00:27:53,979
Does it hurt?

386
00:27:57,059 --> 00:27:58,919
There's sand all over you.

387
00:27:58,919 --> 00:28:00,619
It's fine.

388
00:28:04,020 --> 00:28:06,400
Come on, let's go to the lounge room.

389
00:28:13,199 --> 00:28:15,360
Look at them.

390
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:17,740
They're in front of so many people.

391
00:28:17,740 --> 00:28:20,859
She's not reserved like how a female celebrity should be at all.

392
00:28:20,859 --> 00:28:23,420
When my boyfriend came, did I act that way?

393
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:24,900
Of course not.

394
00:28:24,900 --> 00:28:28,579
You just stayed in the lounge room and maintained your poise completely.

395
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:36,310
Aren't you on a business trip? How can you visit me?

396
00:28:36,310 --> 00:28:38,660
Is it around the area?

397
00:28:39,460 --> 00:28:42,859
If you can't tell me, you don't need to.

398
00:28:42,859 --> 00:28:44,418
I can tell you now.

399
00:28:44,418 --> 00:28:48,180
I just finished my mission yesterday. I left this morning.

400
00:28:48,180 --> 00:28:50,800
Were you really in this desert?

401
00:28:51,980 --> 00:28:54,460
Around 200 km away.

402
00:28:54,460 --> 00:28:56,239
200 km?

403
00:28:56,239 --> 00:28:58,217
It was so close.

404
00:29:00,260 --> 00:29:03,080
It's fine. You just didn't come at a good time.

405
00:29:03,080 --> 00:29:04,460
I have to shoot all day.

406
00:29:04,460 --> 00:29:06,379
And I have one more scene at night.

407
00:29:06,379 --> 00:29:08,090
But tomorrow, I can rest during the day.

408
00:29:08,090 --> 00:29:09,570
We can go around the nearby area.

409
00:29:09,579 --> 00:29:13,740
Treat it as a desert tour paid by the company.

410
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:15,240
Jingjing.

411
00:29:18,579 --> 00:29:22,320
I must go to the airport at 6 PM tonight and return to Shanghai with my colleagues.

412
00:29:22,320 --> 00:29:24,161
I have a meeting early tomorrow morning.

413
00:29:25,819 --> 00:29:27,940
Are you leaving today?

414
00:29:29,579 --> 00:29:30,979
Yes.

415
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:00,909
I'm sorry.

416
00:30:04,157 --> 00:30:06,576
Why are you sorry?

417
00:30:06,576 --> 00:30:09,060
I'm busy too, aren't I?

418
00:30:15,540 --> 00:30:19,793
After filming wraps up, I must take a good rest for two months.

419
00:30:19,793 --> 00:30:21,279
Okay.

420
00:30:21,279 --> 00:30:23,660
I should have more free time then.

421
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:25,252
Really?

422
00:30:25,760 --> 00:30:27,900
At least I don't need to go on a business trip.

423
00:30:28,840 --> 00:30:30,679
You haven't eaten, right?

424
00:30:30,679 --> 00:30:33,421
I'll ask Xiao Zhu to get us two portions of lunches.

425
00:30:35,212 --> 00:30:36,612
It's fine.

426
00:30:37,869 --> 00:30:39,948
Let's get down to business first.

427
00:30:42,180 --> 00:30:43,780
Business?

428
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,940
What business?

429
00:31:02,779 --> 00:31:07,879
I... have two more scenes in the afternoon.

430
00:31:09,980 --> 00:31:12,920
My make-up can't be ruined.

431
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:19,780
I can do it by myself.

432
00:31:45,080 --> 00:31:48,398
Jingjing, is he your friend?

433
00:31:48,398 --> 00:31:52,120
No. He's a maintenance worker I hired.

434
00:31:54,478 --> 00:31:56,980
- Director. 
 - Director.

435
00:31:57,580 --> 00:31:59,339
Go on.

436
00:32:00,984 --> 00:32:02,160
What is he installing?

437
00:32:02,162 --> 00:32:03,819
I don't know.

438
00:32:03,819 --> 00:32:05,619
A signal booster.

439
00:32:06,540 --> 00:32:09,140
I know that. Xiao Huang, didn't we install that?

440
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:11,360
We did, it's that one.

441
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:14,579
But it doesn't quite work. It's pretty useless.

442
00:32:14,579 --> 00:32:15,740
Jingjing told me already.

443
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:18,220
There are mixed qualities in the market for this equipment.

444
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:20,480
You might have gotten one with bad quality.

445
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,660
You can remove it later.

446
00:32:21,660 --> 00:32:23,460
A bad quality equipment isn't of much use.

447
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:25,379
The base station interference is bigger.

448
00:32:25,379 --> 00:32:26,660
Then will this work?

449
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:27,819
I think so.

450
00:32:27,819 --> 00:32:30,058
I asked my friend who's a specialist to make it.

451
00:32:30,058 --> 00:32:33,339
Later on, if you film in another place, you can bring it along too.

452
00:32:33,339 --> 00:32:35,680
It's very easy to install.

