00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:37,820
   

454
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:47,253
   

455
00:32:47,253 --> 00:32:49,020
 I missed you, too. 

456
00:32:52,819 --> 00:32:54,319
It's good to go now.

457
00:32:56,786 --> 00:32:58,677
Director, it works.

458
00:32:58,677 --> 00:32:59,979
Really?

459
00:32:59,979 --> 00:33:01,723
It really works.

460
00:33:02,339 --> 00:33:03,760
Thank you so much.

461
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:06,179
You solved a big problem for us.

462
00:33:06,179 --> 00:33:07,739
You're welcome.

463
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:11,499
I'm doing it for myself, too.

464
00:33:11,499 --> 00:33:14,361
It's too long to lose contact for over ten hours every day.

465
00:33:14,361 --> 00:33:17,063
Yes, that's a bit long.

466
00:33:17,063 --> 00:33:18,020
Yes.

467
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:20,819
And Jingjing told me that you have a lot of night scenes later on.

468
00:33:20,819 --> 00:33:22,599
Yes, that's right.

469
00:33:23,539 --> 00:33:25,717
 Are you done filming today? 

470
00:33:25,717 --> 00:33:27,260
No, we're still filming. Look, today...

471
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:30,401
So what if I have a lot of night scenes? Can't you sleep if you don't see me?

472
00:33:31,639 --> 00:33:33,439
I can't sleep well.

473
00:33:34,239 --> 00:33:36,323
You're such a sweet talker.

474
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:41,040
Do you want another one?

475
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,180
Xiao Huang.

476
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,900
Hurry, arrange for someone

477
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:53,299
to treat Jingjing and her boyfriend to dinner tonight.

478
00:33:53,299 --> 00:33:55,399
- Thank them well. 
 - All right.

479
00:33:55,399 --> 00:33:56,779
Thank you, Director.

480
00:33:56,779 --> 00:34:00,080
But I must reach the airport by 6 p.m. tonight. I must leave at 2:30 p.m. at the latest.

481
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:01,880
Are you in such a hurry?

482
00:34:01,901 --> 00:34:04,819
If you're leaving at 2:30 p.m., Ms. Jingjing is shooting a scene at 1 p.m.

483
00:34:04,819 --> 00:34:07,344
Then your visit here...

484
00:34:08,640 --> 00:34:11,900
This... This is what we'll do. Let's push back the afternoon shoot for an hour.

485
00:34:11,900 --> 00:34:13,401
There's no need, Director. It's fine. Let's not delay filming.

486
00:34:13,401 --> 00:34:16,860
I know what I'm doing. It won't get delayed. It's decided then.

487
00:34:16,860 --> 00:34:18,339
It's decided. Thank you.

488
00:34:18,339 --> 00:34:20,494
It's decided.

